### Development environment setting
```bash
$ pdm add requests
$ pdm add -dG test pytest pytest-cov
```

```bash
$ docker build -t president_speech:0.2.0 .
$ docker run -d --name roh-moo-hyun020 -v "$PWD":/usr/src/app president_speech:0.2.0
```
